cent. Language is a tool to communicate, but very often people are afraid to speak because they are ashame of their accent. Uncle Siu&rsquo;s accent is an art and I love it. But fundamentally, authenticity is the most important part of a speech, people care about YOU, your story, your feeling. I have an Indian friend that speak very well English with heavy Indian accent, and usually my mom could only pick up 50% of what an English man speaks, but she understood completely what my Indian friend said, wasn&rsquo;t that beautiful? <br />\n<br />\nWould we make fun of Gandhi&rsquo;s English speech? Or Nelson Mandela&rsquo;s speech? <br />\n<br />\nI ain&rsquo;t a fan of William Chan. But I respect what this dude has achieved, he worked hard for it. And I&rsquo;m proud that a boy who was born and raised in Hong Kong has reached this international stage. <br />\n<br />\nA speech from Gandhi - <a href=\"https://youtu.be/8yMcNubXqc4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8yMcNubXqc4&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=1b8c6172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8yMcNubXqc4</a>"},{"pid":"2d3a13e02fd41d37e88a0d6c02663623fe0303d2","tid":1182220,"uid":249475,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35427717d5be385a2a1c3c66ddf861d7f7faa1c6","tid":1182220,"uid":40470,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"睇樣子啦<br />\n<br />\n你揀chok口音蕭縮縮樣<br />\n<br />\n定係陳霆偉柒式口音？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"我要陳霆偉柒式口音算